abstract: Mr. and Mrs. Melvin Schreiber of Sands Point, L.I., have announced the engagement of their daughter, Jill Amy Schreiber, to Loren Brett Kleinman, son of Mr. and Mrs. George Kleinman of New Rochelle, N.Y. The wedding is planned for June.
